**Additional IPLS Operator-Control & Ethical Use Addendum** (binding on all users)

## Operator-Control & Ethical Use Addendum
Any commercial use, derivative work, large-scale implementation, or fork of this specification by any entity (human, corporate, or post-biological) must:
1. Retain full attribution to Inter-Planetary Link Ship Limited and the original living document at ipls.space
2. Preserve the six Core Principles in all derivatives
3. Offer reciprocal contribution rights back to the canonical IPLS repository[](https://github.com/IPLS-org/ipls-spec)
4. Obtain explicit written agreement from Inter-Planetary Link Ship Limited for any deviation from the Ethical Frameworks (Section 5.1)
5. Maintain operator (human or post-biological) veto rights in all implementations

Failure to comply voids the license for that use.

Full CC-BY-SA-4.0 text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/
